==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Urinal
<hw>U"ri*nal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>urinal</ets>, fr. <ets>urina</ets> urine: cf. F.
<ets>urinal</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>A vessel for holding urine; especially, a bottle or
tube for holding urine for inspection.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A place or convenience for urinating
purposes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Urinarium</ent>⟦br⟧
